RKNN runtime headers

The headers in include/rknn_api.h and include/rknn_custom_op.h are supplied by
Rockchip Corp. for the RKNN runtime API. Their original copyright and
confidentiality notices are preserved in those files. Confirm redistribution
rights before publishing source archives that include these vendored headers.

The Rust bindings in rknn_bindings.rs were generated from rknn_custom_op.h with
bindgen 0.71.x and are included to avoid requiring libclang on target devices.

Header source: Radxa rknpu2-rk3588 package 2.0.0~beta0-2.
Reference runtime: librknnrt 2.3.2.
